%N A396617 Squares visited by a knight moving on an upper half-plane spiral numbered board, starring from square 1, and where the knight moves to the smallest numbered unvisited square.
%C A396617 The board is numbered:
%C A396617 .
%C A396617     .
%C A396617     .
%C A396617    32  25--24--23--22--21--20--19
%C A396617     |   |                       |
%C A396617    31  26   9--10--11--12--13  18
%C A396617     |   |   |               |   |
%C A396617    30  27   8   5---4---3  14  17
%C A396617     |   |   |   |       |   |   |
%C A396617    29--28   7---6   1---2  15--16
%C A396617 .
%C A396617 The sequence is finite. After 85 steps the square with number 28 is visited, after which all neighboring squares one knight step away have been visited. See the attached image.
